&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.imgflip.com/9np2o0.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Career progress&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can only agree.&lt;/p&gt;

