&lt;p&gt;Symptoms associated with ‚Äúbrain rot‚Äù include reduced attention spans, impaired memory, decreased critical thinking skills, and disrupted sleep patterns. For instance, activities like endless scrolling through memes, watching short-form videos without educational value, or engaging in superficial online interactions are commonly cited as contributors to this cognitive decline.&lt;/p&gt;

